                <p rend="flushleft">1. <hi rend="italic">Meeting of the Peace Conference</hi>
                </p>
                <p>After an exchange of views, it was <hi rend="italic">agreed</hi> to continue the
                    discussion of this question at the next meeting of the Foreign Ministers.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">2. <hi rend="italic">Time of the Next Council Meeting</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Foreign Ministers <hi rend="italic">decided</hi> to meet in private session
                    at 5 p.m. on the same day.</p>
